        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Limit Ongoing Shortages and Stabilize Supply Act of 2020 or the LOSS Act of 2020 </b></p> <p>This bill addresses drug shortages, including by requiring drug manufacturers to conduct risk assessments and implement risk-mitigation plans with respect to such shortages.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
